game.name: Mommy Doctor Check Up
game.description:
This beautiful mommy is pretty excited for her new baby on this planet. The cute girl can deliver her baby anytime so she needs to go to the doctor for a regular check-up. She has visited a hospital where you are a doctor who is going to examine her. Do you think that you are able to tackle this medical job on your hand? Join Mommy Doctor Check Up and be prepared to make sure that everything is going well! Also check the health of baby insider her. 
When you click the play button, you would find out the pregnant woman sitting on the medical chair. The left side of the screen shows you the medical equipment and tools and the ride right side of the screen will show you the items through which you have to perform her ultrasound. Use all the tools including thermometer, tonometer, BP machine and also check out the heart beat of the mommy using stethoscope in this HTML5 doctor game! Measure the belly of the mommy and make sure that everything is going well. 
In the next stage, you have to take care of her vitamins, belly tattoos and help her baby enjoy the lovely music. It is your responsibility to make sure that her baby is also healthy by giving her a fast routine check-up. Try to follow the instructions to complete all the tasks successfully in this online medical simulation game! Examine the health of mommy and her baby by following the proper instructions!
